\s UHORAHO N’UMUCO WAWE
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Uhoraho n’umuco wanje, amurikira ibirenge vyanje, n’ahimbarizw’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd Izina \bd*\bd ryiwe, ni ryo ryampaye kubana nawe.\bd*
\pc \bdit ./.Ubu ntegereje kandi nihanganye kuzambikw’umubiri udapfa\bdit*\bdit ./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ntegereje izuka ry’Abera, no kubona Umukiza wanje, twibonanire hirya mw’ijuru, ibi nivyo vyizigiro mfise.\bd*
\pc \bdit ./.Ubu ntegereje kandi nihanganye kuzambikw’umubiri udapfa./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Uhoraho n’umwungere wanje, ntaco nzokena mur’iyi nzira, naho umwijima wonsugereza, inkingi y’umuriro n’itara ryanje\bd*
\pc \bdit ./.Ubu ntegereje kandi nihanganye kuzambikw’umubiri udapfa./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Nyenyeri yo ku kagoroba, suk’umuco mu bana bawe, bahumuke babon’inzira, ubahe n’amavuta asagutse.\bd*
\pc \bdit ./.Ubu ntegereje kandi nihanganye kuzambikw’umubiri udapfa./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Yesu abwira abamwizeye ati : ni je Muco w’ukuri, n’umwungere w’igura intama, utandiye wese ntaronk’ubugingo.\bd*
\pc \bdit ./.Ubu ntegereje kandi nihanganye kuzambikw’umubiri udapfa./.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Nyenyeri yo mu gaturuturu, ah’ushitse nta mwiza uhaba, tugushimiy’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ijambo uduha, ni ryo gari rizodushitsa mw’ijuru.\bd*
\pc \bdit ./.Ubu ntegereje kandi nihanganye kuzambikw’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit umubiri udapfa./.\bdit*
